255
00:19:11,335 --> 00:19:12,251
Effrayant.

256
00:19:14,025 --> 00:19:15,360
Alors tu me parles?

257
00:19:16,206 --> 00:19:17,100
Ouais.

258
00:19:18,556 --> 00:19:21,912
Il se passe des trucs et je ne sais pas quoi faire.

259
00:19:22,925 --> 00:19:25,352
